{"tid":1720463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣］建議和理非中環人放lunch時印多小小嘢","createTime":"2019-11-14T11:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T01:59:59.000Z","uid":45190,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b3e6604a6b4d41a6e6c116feede2c301753d3f19","tid":1720463,"uid":45190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:05:50.000Z","msg":"話說呢幾日發夢放lunch時，都有啲鬼佬清走我地嘅rb，佢地主要重複呢幾點<br />\n<br />\n1. 點解我地要破壞條路<br />\n2. 點解我地要set rb <br />\n<br />\n今日都見有手足派英文文宣，但如果我地每人印十張， 同埋target 食花生嘅西裝鬼佬而唔係已經著曬黑衫嘅外國人手足，明白大家都有唔同原因罷唔到工，但仍見好多西裝同埋OL放lunch 戴口罩支持，比起大家齋企，不如每人印小小嘢，食飯時派下文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"4f00cd590bd8cfa9c225263b7c203cc8b2d74acf","tid":1720463,"uid":220356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:06:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ccd38fc2e5a4b2f7cfb1d265eb5dfbc3faacec4f","tid":1720463,"uid":45190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F9GJODR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF9GJODR.jpg&h=e7f90ad1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bdoW8DS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbdoW8DS.jpg&h=def710a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RmP7vSc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmP7vSc.jpg&h=09c22a6f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2dgpcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2dgpcd.jpg&h=d5c6470f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JA2AELz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJA2AELz.jpg&h=345a0e87&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tGLbc5A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2